OL,3,C'Never take peace for granted':
OL,4,CSurvivor of Bosnian War visits Jersey
OL,6,FA Bosnian man who was forced to flee
OL,7,Fthe country as a child has visited
OL,8,FJersey as part of the island's
OL,9,FHolocaust Memorial Day commemorations.
OL,11,FIn 2020, Smajo Beso founded the , a
OL,12,Fcharity that spreads awareness about
OL,13,Fthe atrocities of the Bosnian War.
OL,15,FHe was also recently honoured with an
OL,16,FOBE for services to genocide education
OL,17,Fand commemoration in the 2023 New Year
OL,18,FHonours list.
