OL,3,C'Never take peace for granted':
OL,4,CSurvivor of Bosnian War visits Jersey
OL,6,F"Learning from the Holocaust, and
OL,7,Fsubsequent genocides like the one in
OL,8,FBosnia, can enhance our understanding
OL,9,Fof possible warning signs or patterns
OL,10,Fand, most importantly, it can better
OL,11,Fequip us to actively work towards
OL,12,Fpreventing future atrocities.
OL,14,F"Peace isn't simply the absence of
OL,15,Fwar; it is our everyday actions
OL,16,Fthrough which war is made less likely.
OL,17,FThat is the true nature of peace."
